  "text": "Genetically obese ob/ob mice and wild-type C57BL/6J mice were purchased from Charles River Japan (Yokohama, Japan). The adipose SVF was prepared by collagenase digestion from perigonadal fat tissue of both strains at 12 weeks of age. [CITATION_1] The procedure was performed under pentobarbital anesthesia (30 mg/kg). All of the animal experiments were conducted in accordance with the guidelines of Tokyo Medical and Dental University Committee on Animal Research (No. 0050140).",
